   - (docs) add missing references  [Karel Zak]
   - (docs) fix typo, remove unused reference  [Karel Zak]
   - (parser) fix memory leak on error before end-of-file  [Karel Zak]
   - (umount) FS lookup refactoring  [Karel Zak]
